msgctxt "practice.1.goal"
msgid "Your code should remove all the crates in the array using a while loop."
msgstr "你的代码应该用 while 循环来移除数组中所有的箱子。"

#: course/lesson-23-append-to-arrays/lesson.bbcode:103
