#: course/lesson-24-access-array-indices/lesson.bbcode:60
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Arrays come with a [glossary term=\"member function\"] named [code]size()[/code]. You can call it on the array anytime to know its [i]current[/i] size."
msgstr "数组自带一个名为 [code]size()[/code] 的成员函数。你可以随时在数组上调用它，来获取数组 [i]当前[/i] 的大小。"

#: course/lesson-24-access-array-indices/lesson.bbcode:63
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "text"
msgid "The maximum index you can access in an array is [code]array.size() - 1[/code]: it's the last item in the array."
msgstr "你能访问的最大索引是 [code]array.size() - 1[/code]，它指向数组的最后一项。"

